    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The study on the history of origin and evolvement of buildings, using varied research methods such as photography, study of literature and archives, iconographical, cartographical and in situ-research and the study of oral histories.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
